Package: libjs-sphinxdoc
Version: 1.1.3
Revision: 1
###
Depends: <<
	sphinx-py27,
	libjs-jquery (>= 1.4),
	libjs-underscore
<<
###
Source: none
###
CompileScript: <<
echo None;
<<
InstallScript: <<
#!/bin/sh -ex
install -d -m0755 %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/1.0/

touch %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/index
cat << EOF >> %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/index
# <filename> [min-version]
1.0/doctools.js
1.0/jquery.js
1.0/searchtools.js
1.0/sidebar.js
1.0/theme_extras.js
1.0/underscore.js
EOF

ln -s %p/lib/python2.7/site-packages/sphinx/themes/basic/static/doctools.js %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/1.0/doctools.js
ln -s %p/share/javascript/jquery/jquery.js %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/1.0/jquery.js 
ln -s %p/lib/python2.7/site-packages/sphinx/themes/basic/static/searchtools.js_t %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/1.0/searchtools.js
ln -s %p/lib/python2.7/site-packages/sphinx/themes/default/static/sidebar.js %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/1.0/sidebar.js
ln -s %p/lib/python2.7/site-packages/sphinx/themes/scrolls/static/theme_extras.js %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/1.0/theme_extras.js
ln -s %p/share/javascript/underscore/underscore.js %i/share/javascript/sphinxdoc/1.0/underscore.js 
<<
###
Description: JavaScript support for Sphinx documentation
DescDetail: <<
Sphinx is a tool for producing documentation for Python projects, using
reStructuredText as markup language.
.
This package provides JavaScript code for documentation generated by Sphinx.
<<
